## üìÇ CODE DESCRIPTION:
1) AI_Based_Security_monitoring_For_deviceSec.py: Uses your webcam to recognize the authorized face and locks the device if an unauthorized person or no face is seen for 10 seconds.
2) face_recognition_training.py: Trains a face recognition KNN model from images in the "dataset" folder and saves it as "face_model.pkl".
3) monitor_embeddings.py: Monitors the webcam for authorized/unauthorized/no-face states, sends events to an API, speaks a warning, and locks the screen after 10 seconds of unauthorized/no user.
4) recognize_faces.py: Recognizes faces from the webcam using the saved model and shows the predicted name on the video.
5) test_face_detection.py: Simply detects faces from the webcam and draws rectangles around them.
